# Dry Run

```check name="health-check"
curl -sf http://localhost/health
```

```step name="deploy" rollback="undo-deploy"
  timeout: 120s
  confirm: production
---
echo "deploying"
```

```step name="verify"
echo "verifying"
```

```rollback name="undo-deploy"
echo "rolling back deploy"
```
